# 重構計畫：刪除廢棄的舊版導航系統程式碼

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **策略：路線 A（保留 JSON 格式，刪除行為邏輯）**
> JSON 地圖檔格式不變動，PathNode 瘦身為純 DTO，移除所有已被 Edge-Driven A* 取代的舊邏輯。

## 預估影響

| 指標 | Before | After |
|:---|:---|:---|
| [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs) | ~1390 行 (60KB) | ~950 行 (~40KB) |
| [PathNode.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs) | ~197 行 | ~95 行 |
| [SmartRopeNavigator.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/SmartRopeNavigator.cs) | ~150 行 | **刪除整個檔案** |
| 可刪減總行數 | — | **~500+ 行** |

---

## Phase 1：PathNode.cs → 純 DTO

#### [MODIFY] [PathNode.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs)

**保留（讀 JSON 用）：**
- [Position](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MapEditor.cs#140-157), [Index](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MapEditor.cs#368-392), [Keys](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#453-478), `IsBreak`
- [Action](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#108-125) (computed property via [DetermineAction()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#68-96))
- [DetermineAction()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#68-96) (private method)
- [ToString()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#1523-1524)

**刪除（舊版行為邏輯）：**
- `LastVisitTime` 屬性
- `FailedAttempts` 屬性
- `IsBlacklisted` 計算屬性
- [GetPriority()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#123-188) 方法 (~65 行)
- [MarkVisited()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#106-114) 方法
- [MarkFailed()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#115-122) 方法
- [Reset()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#97-105) 方法

