## Phase 2：PathPlanningTracker.cs → 移除舊版欄位與方法

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs)

**刪除欄位：**
- `_ropeNavigator` (SmartRopeNavigator) — 已被 [InjectRopeEdges()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#274-342) 取代
- `_triggeredActionIndices` (HashSet) — 舊版循序導航用
- `_currentPathIndex` — 舊版循序導航索引

**刪除方法：**
- [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1392-1410) (L1213-1230) — 舊版熱力圖，依賴已刪的 [GetPriority()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathNode.cs#123-188)
- [FindClosestPathNodeIndex()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1335-1360) (L1335-1359) — 舊版最近點搜尋
- [SetPlannedPath(List<SdPoint>)](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#393-412) (L365-383) — 純座標版載入（無人呼叫或可由 [LoadMap](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#485-501) 取代）

**清理建構子：**
- 移除 `_ropeNavigator = new SmartRopeNavigator();`

**清理 [InitializePathState()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#585-631)：**
- 移除 `_triggeredActionIndices.Clear();`

**清理 [Dispose()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/PathPlanningManager.cs#218-238)：**
- 移除 `_triggeredActionIndices.Clear();`

**清理 [SetActiveEdge()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1051-1132)：**
- 移除 `_currentPathIndex = legacyIndex;`

**清理 [ForceAdvanceTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1302-1317)：**
- 移除 `_currentTarget.MarkVisited();` 呼叫

**🔧 修正 [UpdatePathState()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1373-1503)（無參數版本）：**
- 將 `CurrentPathState.CurrentWaypointIndex = _currentPathIndex;` 改為 `_currentEdgeIndex`
- 此方法由 [ForceAdvanceTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1302-1317) 呼叫，刪 `_currentPathIndex` 後會 CS0103

