## Phase 4：更新下游消費者

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningManager.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/PathPlanningManager.cs)
- 刪除 [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1392-1410) 方法 (L204-207)
- 刪除 [SetPlannedPath()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#393-412) 轉發方法 (L166 附近，如存在)

#### [MODIFY] [MainForm.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs)
- 移除呼叫 [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1392-1410) 的熱力圖渲染邏輯 (L1331 附近)
- 移除 `n.IsBlacklisted` 引用

#### [MODIFY] [MinimapViewer.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MinimapViewer.cs)
- 🔧 `GetPriorityColor()` 簽名移除 `isBlacklisted` 參數：
  - Before: `GetPriorityColor(float priority, bool isBlacklisted, bool isCurrentTarget)`
  - After: `GetPriorityColor(float priority, bool isCurrentTarget)`
- 刪除方法內 `if (isBlacklisted) return Color.Black;` 分支
- 🔧 更新呼叫端：`GetPriorityColor(wp.Priority, wp.IsBlacklisted, wp.IsCurrentTarget)` → `GetPriorityColor(wp.Priority, wp.IsCurrentTarget)`

#### [MODIFY] [PathVisualizationModels.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Visualization/PathVisualizationModels.cs)
- 移除 `IsBlacklisted` 屬性
- 移除建構子中 `isBlacklisted` 參數與賦值

